.SH OPTIONS
.HP
\fB\-a\fR <cmdlist>,
.TP
\fB\-\-admin\fR <cmdlist>
space separate list of allowed admin commands.
An ! before a command disabled it.
default: 'flush_cache';
available: flush_cache, purge_cache, shutdown
.HP
\fB\-c\fR <path>,
